===Usage notes===
* In mainland China, this character, <big>逕</big> is considered a {{w|Variant Chinese character|variant}} traditional form of {{l|zh|徑}}. The usage of <big>逕</big> is replaced by the orthodox form {{l|zh|徑}} which is simplified as {{l|zh|径}}.
* In the {{w|Song dynasty}} dictionary, {{w|Jiyun}} 《{{lw|zh|集韻}}》, <big>逕</big> is also listed as a {{w|Variant Chinese character|variant form}} of {{l|zh|徑}}. However, in modern Taiwan, <big>逕</big> and {{l|zh|徑}} are considered as two different characters. <!-- Refer http://dict.variants.moe.edu.tw/variants/rbt/word_attribute.rbt?quote_code=QTAxMjg5LTAwNA -->

